        "text": "|  |  |  |  |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| **Sisterstone Items** | **Hardness** | **HP** | **BT** |\n| **Thin Items** |\n| Low-grade | 6 | 18 | 9 |\n| Standard-grade | 8 | 24 | 12 |\n| High-grade | 10 | 36 | 18 |\n| **Items** |\n| Low-grade | 10 | 28 | 14 |\n| Standard-grade | 12 | 40 | 20 |\n| High-grade | 15 | 54 | 27 |\n| **Structures** |\n| Low-grade | 20 | 56 | 28 |\n| Standard-grade | 24 | 80 | 40 |\n| High-grade | 30 | 108 | 54 |\n\n  \n*Rules for Special Materials*",
        "type": "section"
      }
